{"categories":["service-promotion","seasonal-promotion","home_garden","spring"],"collections":"","description":"This email template is perfect for those in the gardening and home goods sectors looking to promote their services or products during the spring and summer seasons. With a focus on the outdoors, the template beautifully captures the essence of a lush green lawn and vibrant plants thriving in the summer sun. It is designed to evoke the joy of yard work and the satisfaction of cultivating a personal garden. With a color palette that leans heavily on shades of green and yellow, it encapsulates the warmth and growth associated with agriculture in the warmer months. Ideal for seasonal promotions, this template is your key to connecting with those who find solace in the tranquility of their backyard gardens.","short_description":"Promote your gardening services, seasonal offers, and home goods with our vibrant summer email template. Ideal for those in the gardening industry, it highlights the beauty of flourishing plants, lush green lawns, and outdoor activities. Connect with your audience through joyful yellow design elements and the charm of yard work. ","designer":{"avatar_url":"https://d1oco4z2z1fhwp.cloudfront.net/designers/melissa.jpg","description":"Hi! My name is Melissa Hickman. I'm an industrial & organizational psychologist, with several years of digital marketing experience. I focus on UX & aesthetic design. I'm based out of Boulder, Colorado. I love working with eCommerce brands and creating high-converting Shopify stores & email campaigns. Aside from my professional life, I love fitness, nutrition & getting outside with the dogs.","short_description":"","display_name":"Melissa Hickman","id":"melissa-hickman"},"html_data":"<!DOCTYPE html><html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" lang=\"en\"><head><title></title><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><meta name=